Qt 4.8.7 and Qt 5.x are supported. Qt 4.7.4 may function.

Homebrew is required for OS X.

If header (h) or interface (ui) files have changed, please perform
a distclean before building BiblioteQ.

Absolute cleaning:
make distclean or mingw32-make distclean

FreeBSD:
qmake -o Makefile biblioteq.freebsd.pro (Qt 4.x)
or
qmake -o Makefile biblioteq.freebsd.qt5.pro (Qt 5.x)
or
qmake-qt4 -o Makefile biblioteq.freebsd.pro
or
qmake-qt5 -o Makefile biblioteq.freebsd.qt5.pro
gmake

Linux:
qmake -o Makefile biblioteq.pro (Qt 4.x)
or
qmake -o Makefile biblioteq.qt5.pro (Qt 5.x)
or
qmake-qt4 -o Makefile biblioteq.pro
or
qmake-qt5 -o Makefile biblioteq.qt5.pro
make

OS X Qt 4.x:
qmake -o Makefile biblioteq.osx.pro
make
sudo make install
sudo cp -r ./BiblioteQ.app /Applications/BiblioteQ.d/.

OS X Qt 5.x:
qmake -o Makefile biblioteq.osx.qt5.pro
sudo make install
sudo cp -r ./BiblioteQ.app /Applications/BiblioteQ_Qt5.d/.

Windows:
qmake -o Makefile biblioteq.win.qt5.pro
make or mingw32-make
